				</dl>
			</div>
			<div class="postright">
				<h3> Re: Want to set up internal bittorrent</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>peer to peer is not client-server. Hence there really is no server except for the trackers. Some clients (such as azureus) also provide tracker functionality, if you need a standalone tracker i would suggest <a href="http://erdgeist.org/arts/software/opentracker/" rel="nofollow">http://erdgeist.org/arts/software/opentracker/</a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="postsignature"><hr />Az dev</div>
			</div>
